OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,8,Fpatchy low cloud and fog in the east.
OL,9,FCold with patchy frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FOvernight mist and low cloud
OL,12,Fsoon clearing to leave a dry day with
OL,13,Fplenty of sunshine. Warm by afternoon.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,16,Fmostly dry and settled with plenty of
OL,17,Fsunshine, warm by afternoon. Patchy
OL,18,Fovernight low cloud in the north and
OL,19,Feast. Chance of the odd light shower
OL,20,Fon Sunday.
